<section
  id="about"
  class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden"
  style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600047508788-786f3865b4ef?w=1920&q=80'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-attachment: fixed;"
>
  <!-- Warm elegant overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-stone-900/90 via-stone-800/75 to-stone-900/85"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/54534654654.jpeg"
            alt="Your Palm Beach Broker"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border-2 border-gold rounded-sm -z-10"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-sans text-gold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Meet Danieyis Jimenez</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white font-light leading-tight mb-6">
          Your Palm Beach<br />
          <span class="text-gold">Broker</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gold mb-8"></div>

        <div class="space-y-5 font-sans text-white/85 leading-relaxed text-base">
          <p>A world where real estate can sometimes lack integrity, my goal is simple: to treat every deal with honesty, professionalism, and care. Every client, every property, and every transaction matters to me.</p>
          <p>Real estate, for me, is more than just a career or a business. It's something I genuinely enjoy every day. I love the challenge, the negotiation, and most of all helping people find what could become one of the best deals or opportunities of their lives.</p>
          <p>I approach every transaction as if it were my own. I negotiate strongly for my clients and always look out for their best interests, protecting them every step of the way.</p>
          <p>I am committed to building long-lasting relationships and making sure my clients feel confident, protected, and happy throughout the entire process.</p>
          <p>I'm also a mother of two beautiful children, and because of that I truly understand the importance of stability and creating a place that feels like home for a family.</p>
          <p>Outside of real estate, I enjoy training at the gym, running, and reading a good book. I believe in discipline, growth, and constantly becoming a better version of myself.</p>
          <p>I take full ownership of my business, and I make myself available to my clients whenever they need me.</p>
          <p>If you're looking for an agent who will truly represent you and fight for your best interests like no other, feel free to contact me. I'll make it happen for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block bg-gold text-white font-sans text-xs tracking-widest uppercase py-4 px-8 hover:bg-gold/90 transition-all duration-300">
            Work With Me
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/yourpalmbeachbroker/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-white text-white font-sans text-xs tracking-widest uppercase py-4 px-6 hover:bg-white hover:text-forest transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/></svg>
            Instagram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
